<H1>Kotlin Spring Excel Report Generator</H1>

<BlockQuote>
    <BlockQuoteContent>
        This page documents a Kotlin-based Spring Boot 3 application that connects to an SQLite database,
        fetches metric data, and generates an Excel file using a predefined template.
        It serves as a template project for CLI-based data export utilities.
    </BlockQuoteContent>
    <BlockQuoteFooter>
        The goal is to provide a reusable template project for generating Excel in Java/Kotlin.
    </BlockQuoteFooter>
</BlockQuote>

